reviews.content:
A good, fun, exciting and nonsense film; tells the story of two brothers who want to pay the overdue tax from the orphanage they were raised in;

At first I didn't give a damn about the movie, but suddenly it gets frantic and fun; the film has everything and in good measure, chase, comedy, drama, good music, several musical celebrities decided to make the film and it was sensational; is a movie to catch popcorn lie on the couch and enjoy without fear of being happy

Mandatory film for all and all ages!
